'''仙女木屬'''（學名：{{lang|la|''Dryas''}}），為[[蔷薇科|蔷薇科]]的一屬常绿多年生小灌木，原产于北美、欧洲和亚洲的北极地区，也见于阿尔卑斯山区。其学名来自希腊神话中的宁芙[[德律阿得斯|德律阿得斯]]。它原本属于[[蔷薇亚科|蔷薇亚科]]，现属于[[仙女木亚科|仙女木亚科]]<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Potter D, Eriksson T, Evans RC, Oh S, ((Smedmark JEE)), Morgan DR, Kerr M, Robertson KR, Arsenault M, Dickinson TA, Campbell CS | year = 2007 | title = Phylogeny and classification of Rosaceae | journal = Plant Systematics and Evolution | volume = 266 | issue = 1–2 | pages = 5–43 | doi = 10.1007/s00606-007-0539-9}}.</ref>。

==下属物种==
该属无争议的种仅有三个：<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Skrede I, Eidesen PB, Piñeiro Portela R, Brochmann C | year = 2006 | title = Refugia, differentiation and postglacial migration in arctic-alpine Eurasia, exemplified by the mountain avens (''Dryas octopetala'' L.) | journal = Molecular Ecology | volume = 15 | issue = 7 | pages = 1827–1840 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-294X.2006.02908.x| pmid = 16689901 }}</ref><ref name="PlantList">{{cite web | url = http://www.theplantlist.org/1.1/browse/A/Rosaceae/Dryas/ | title = The Plant List entry for ''Dryas'' | date = September 2013 | website = [[The_Plant_List|The Plant List]], v.1.1 | publisher = [[邱园|Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew]] and the [[Missouri_Botanical_Garden|Missouri Botanical Garden]] | accessdate = 14 December 2020 | archive-date = 2017-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170905074412/http://www.theplantlist.org/1.1/browse/A/Rosaceae/Dryas/ }}</ref>
*''[[Dryas_drummondii|Dryas drummondii]]'' <small>Richardson ex Hook.</small>
** var. ''drummondii'' <small>Richardson ex Hook.</small> 
** var. ''tomentosa'' <small>(Farr) L.O. Williams</small> 
